    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains excellent composure with a factory-spec variable M differential lock and a highly communicative steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a detailed subframe inspection to ensure structural integrity under high-torque loads. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its driver-grade status, the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with perfect linear power delivery and zero hesitation. This is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated engineering, ready for the open road.",
